<p>
<lb n="1"/>samasta 25 Aṅka srāhi vikṣī su 13 śūkaruvāre jīarade
<lb n="2" break="no"/>sa deula mogaparikṣā mūlāije pa <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> samasta pāñcapara
<lb n="3" break="no"/>karaṇa samasta vedasiśika narthakavā jīara kṣetrabhitta
<lb n="4" break="no"/>re je riṇa devo ghośimāne kañjara dāsamāhā
<lb n="5"/>kodiṇe deva <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> na kehidhile kauṇa je
<lb n="6" break="no"/>māna pāimāgile bhaṇḍārakū caṭāsa ṭa 100 mā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kro <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Etharvaku Aṣṭalokapāla dharuma sākṣi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> jī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>a samastalokaṅkara sanamata [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
